room_title: Escape room "The Illusionist" by Amazing Escape Room in Bridgewater
room_address: 326 Route 22 West Suites 13/14B Green Brook, New Jersey, NJ 08812
room_description: The Mysterious Malini is one of the greatest magicians of his time. You and your group of aspiring magicians were supposed to be attending The Mysterious Malini’s latest performance but you stumbled into his private parlor and discovered that he is a murderer. He has locked you in the parlor and you now have only 60 min’s until the performance ends and he returns to make you vanish forever.
